data.description: PRICE REDUCTION in this True tropical South Florida Lifestyle Complex- complete with a marina. PRICE REDUCTION! This amazingly priced 1BR/1.5BA interior corner unit is located in the beautiful 55+ Sea Haven complex, that is undergoing  an incredible "head to toe" renovation. Property has a marina w/dockage when available, heated pool, shuffleboard, clubhouse, BBQ - All in a Great Location  w/i walking distance to the beach. Minutes from restaurants, shopping and entertainment. No Rentals for first 2 years of ownership. If utilities are turned on for inspections, they must be in Buyer's name and turned off after inspections Buyer to be responsible for remainder of Special Assessment.  Seller does not accept blind offers or escalation clauses. Seller has no history on the property.
